HEADWORD: Mickle
<hw>Mic"kle</hw> <pr>(m⟦icr⟧k"k'l)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>mikel</ets>, <ets>muchel</ets>, <ets>mochel</ets>,
<ets>mukel</ets>, AS. <ets>micel</ets>, <ets>mycel</ets>; akin to OS.
<ets>mikil</ets>, OHG. <ets>mihil</ets>, <ets>mihhil</ets>, Icel.
<ets>mikill</ets>, <ets>mykill</ets>, Goth. <ets>mikils</ets>, L.
<ets>magnus</ets>, Gr. <grk>me`gas</grk>, gen. <grk>mega`loy</grk>; cf.
